Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:21.10,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.82,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人忧伤的纯粹简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:27.09,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕阳西下时的道场一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.86,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挥洒着汗水练习刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.76,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人发笑的满腔热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:39.06,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有梦想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.96,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般这样大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.39,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:49.32,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝阳东升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.23,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你会在喧闹的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.17,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拼命奔跑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:58.39,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.05,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:04.20,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你会穿过宽阔的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:06.30,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河滩边诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.96,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是这样吧 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:16.63,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.32,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一颗赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:22.49,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守护着重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:25.46,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}脸上透露着决心吧
